<div class="point"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i> Smart Crop Health Insights with AI</h3><p>AI disease detection.</p></div>
<div class="point"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-droplet"></i> Smart Irrigation with IoT</h3><p>Efficient water usage.</p></div>
<div class="point"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-sun-rain"></i> Real-Time Weather Updates</h3><p>Live weather alerts.</p></div>
<div class="point"><h3><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Live GPS Tracking of Deliveries</h3><p>Track orders in real-time.</p></div>
